<item>
            <title>[LU-15133] don&apos;t deactivate OST upon normal precreate error</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15133</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If osp_get_lastfid_from_ost() RPC failed, it will deactivate OST to let user to handle bad OST, but there may be different kinds of errors, some may be trivial, e.g. network issue, it&apos;s not necessary to deactivate OST in such cases. Among all the errors, -EFAULT means reading &lt;tt&gt;LAST_ID&lt;/tt&gt; on OST failed, and it should only deactivate OST in this case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
